# Module 3: GitHub Copilot & Cursor Fundamentals – Participant Guide

## 📝 Overview
Master GitHub Copilot and Cursor for efficient AI pair programming.

## 🎯 Learning Objectives
- Set up and configure GitHub Copilot & Cursor
- Use autocomplete, chat mode, and agent mode for real coding tasks

## 🚀 Activities
1. Setup Copilot and Cursor in Codespaces
2. Practice autocomplete in new vs existing files
3. Bug fixing using chat mode
4. Build a small CLI program using agent mode

## 💬 Discussion
- When is autocomplete ideal?
- When should you escalate to chat or agent mode?
